Nice amber color. lots of carbonation. long lasting head with sticky lacing
Aroma hits you right from the get go.  Dank. Cat pee (in a good way). 
Feels like I'm drinking straight hop juice. Delicious. Dry, mildly bitter finish.
The feel is really where this beer shines...sticky, coats your whole mouth with wonderful hops.
Was glad to finally get a chance to try this one...thanks again jeffgott for the can!
A really excellent DIPA 452 charactersbenjamminjones24, Feb 25, 2016
