4.42/5  rDev -3.1%look: 4.5 | smell: 4.25 | taste: 4.5 | feel: 4.25 |  overall: 4.5azdback, Dec 25, 2015
4.73/5  rDev +3.7%look: 4.75 | smell: 4.75 | taste: 4.75 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.75Bobloblawlawblog11, Dec 24, 2015
