Smell - Hops, citrus, pineapple, pine.  Seems to get stronger and smell better as I continue drinking.
Taste - Piney, with a mild amount of citrus and a great hop bite.  The hops are the last flavor that hit my palate, but they don't linger.  I was amazed at how quickly the aftertaste dies.  Very well balanced beer.
