4.8/5  rDev +5.3%look: 5 | smell: 5 | taste: 4.75 | feel: 4.5 |  overall: 4.75Double Sunshine's little brother. Close enough that it's almost indistinguishable.
LOOK: Honey gold leaning to orange. Dense foamy white head that lingers and coats the glass. Nice lacing. Slightly cloudy. Hold it up to the light and watch some of those bubbles dance.
SMELL: Paradise. Tropical fruits (pineapple, mango, citrus citrus citrus) and light floral notes.
TASTE: Those tropical fruit aromas are there on the taste buds immediately and open in a big way. Bitterness is present on the finish as an assertive bite, but it doesn't linger.
FEEL: Full-bodied. Coats the mouth. Resiny? Sticky? It's full and it clings. 626 charactersfounddrama, Mar 24, 2015
