Pours a brilliant orange with a solid cream colored head. Smells of sweet orange and bready malts. Almost no bitterness with a marmalade flavor. Great mouthfeel, just heavy enough with perfect carbonation. It goes down way too easy for 8%. If this is close to what Double Sunshine is, I understand the hype. 353 charactersunclejazz, Apr 05, 2014
